      <div class="msgContentFrame">When you get down to it, most DPS are lazy tards who don't want to put a single moments thought or effort into the game. They don't want to wait till you have threat, they don't want to wait for healer mana, they don't want to CC, they just want to AOE and wank off to DPS meters. Healers and tanks understand each other, they have a bond. They know that a good run is much more than speed or winning at recount. A good run is about elegant pulls, efficient healing and the pleasure you can get from doing something right. Most DPS don't see this, they just want there frosties as fast as possible. F**ck them, f**k them up their stupid arses. Give me hybrid DPS anyday, they tend to understand.</div>
