      <div class="msgContentFrame">Kavekk, I refer you too &quot;and help the team kill the bosses&quot; regarding your response to my statements about DPS. Of course there is more to being a good player than spamming the set rotation. I thought that was implied in my statement. <br /> <br />Also refer to the word &quot;basic&quot; in reference to your response on my statements about tanking. There are plenty of methods to pull mobs and save your group when things go wonky. By &quot;basic&quot; I mean that there is a certain mean-average TPS that any tank will produce without having to resort to special methods. Tank's TPS sets the limitations of the DPS. <br /> <br />Hope that clears up my previous comments. <br /> <br />In other news.... FOR PONY!<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm">&quot;I'm gonna need to see more math I don't understand to believe all this&quot; <br />日本人彼女募集中 <br /><a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Zede" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Zede">Zede the Undying</a> • <a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Phezz" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Phezz">Phezz, the Insane Kingslayer</a> • <a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Dehlia" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Dehlia">Dehlia the Love Fool</a></span></div></div>
