 IRL (somebody trying to talk to me and I didn't want anyone to die while my attention is divided), maybe I'm having a lag spike, whatever. <br /> <br />The Tank is the leader. He controls the pulls, he controls what is pulled, where. <br /> <br />DPS need to learn this, and learn to leave group if they don't like the Tank's methods.</div>
