      <div class="msgContentFrame">Problem is that people are spoiled - most folks doing heroics are doing them for a specific achievement or frost badges or occasionally a trinket or other item which is still useful to a person with a 5k+ GS - meaning that they just want to get from point A to B as fast as possible so that they can get back to doing whatever they do after they get their daily frost badges. <br /> <br />Next up on the spoiled list is their personal DPS - nothing pisses off a high end DPS more then a tank with a 2k lower GS who forces said DPS to calm down or ends up losing aggro (and God forbid you &quot;cause&quot; someone to die because that DPS pulled a group on his own and you didn't score insta ag on it), so you've got some tantrums there as well. <br /> <br />Finally you've got the healers, who quite frankly are getting lazy and spoiled thanks to so many tanks out there only needing the occasional top off every other pull and even after having pulled a quarter of the instance.  Lazy healers who suddenly discover that they not only have to heal the tank, but also the stupid DPS who insist on going full burn on a mob despite knowing the tank's GS is too low to keep pace get upset real fast at having to actually work during instances again. <br /> <br />So there's the three issues which are causing you problems - peeps upset that you can't give them a 15m run, 5.5k GS DPS who wont/don't want to slow down and healers who suddenly are finding they have to do more then keep the tank targetted and occasionally hit a heal button.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>OK, yeah, maybe us druids are a tad overpowered <br /> <br /><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kl0PQHT34_0&amp;NR" title="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kl0PQHT34_0&amp;NR" rel="external nofollow">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kl0PQHT34_0&amp;NR</a> <br /> <br />You may be a feral druid if... <br /> <br /><a href="http://wow.allakhazam.com/db/class.html?wclass=6;mid=116937588840616132" title="http://wow.allakhazam.com/db/class.html?wclass=6;mid=116937588840616132" rel="external nofollow">http://wow.allakhazam.com/db/class.html?wclass=6;mid=116937588840616132</a> <br /> <br />Great virus links and advice from other users <br /> <br /><a href="/forum.html?forum=21;mid=1233014529277943190;page=1#m1233788962189142490" title="http://wow.allakhazam.com/forum.html?forum=21;mid=1233014529277943190;page=1#m1233788962189142490" rel="external">http://wow.allakhazam.com/forum.html?forum=21;mid=1233014529277943190;page=1#m1233788962189142490</a></div></div>
